OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis change would be 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fa tragedy, says ex-boss    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former John Lewis boss has said it   
OL,6, would be a "tragedy" if the retailer   
OL,7, changed its ownership model, which has 
OL,8, been in staff hands for 70 years.      
OL,10,FAndy Street, managing director from    
OL,11,F2007 to 2016, told the BBC's Sunday    
OL,12,Fwith Laura Kuenssberg that John Lewis  
OL,13,Fwent beyond being a shop.              
OL,15,FThe firm is considering selling a stake
OL,16,Fin its business, meaning it would no   
OL,17,Flonger be fully owned by its employees.
OL,19,FIt comes after the retailer reported a 
OL,20,F#234m loss last year.                  
